      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable vehicle that\u2019s ready to keep you moving? This car is in fair condition and offers great value for anyone seeking a reliable ride! While it shows some honest character and wear from its journeys, it remains a sturdy companion that's prepared for many more miles ahead. It\u2019s a fantastic opportunity to own a functional, honest car at a great price!",
