    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained to ensure a reliable driving experience. The engine starts up easily and runs smoothly, while the transmission provides steady shifts throughout all gears. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing only minor signs of use, and all essential electronics and climate controls are fully functional. On the exterior, the paint maintains a nice shine, though you may find a few small chips or light surface scratches typical for a car of this age. Overall, it is a solid, dependable vehicle that is ready for its next owner with no immediate repairs required.",
