    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014it\u2019s been my pride and joy and has been kept spotless inside and out. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, you've definitely found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 46500.0,
